861
01:09:56,316 --> 01:09:57,985
<i>Peço que acabe com isso.</i>

862
01:10:20,341 --> 01:10:21,468
Tom!

863
01:10:24,762 --> 01:10:26,014
Eu fui usada.

864
01:10:26,139 --> 01:10:29,767
